<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Fundamental Rights</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
	
</head>
<body>

	    <!-- Main Content Section -->
    <main class="container mt-5">
        <section class="text-center">
            <h1>Constitutional Framework</h1>
            <p class="lead">
                The Indian Constitution is the backbone of our democracy, designed to ensure justice, liberty, equality, and fraternity for all citizens.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-5">
            <h2>Key Components of the Framework</h2>
            <div class="row mt-4">
                <!-- Card 1 -->
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card">
                        <img src="/images/preamble.jpeg" class="card-img-top" alt="Preamble">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h4 class="card-title">Preamble</h4>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                The Preamble outlines the ideals and objectives of the Constitution, emphasizing justice, liberty, equality, and fraternity.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Card 2 -->
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card">
                        <img src="images/fundamentalrights.jpeg" class="card-img-top" alt="Fundamental Rights">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h4 class="card-title">Fundamental Rights</h4>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                Fundamental Rights protect the individual liberties of every citizen, ensuring freedom and equality.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Card 3 -->
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card">
                        <img src="images/directiveprinciples.jpeg" class="card-img-top" alt="Directive Principles">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h4 class="card-title">Directive Principles</h4>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                These principles guide the state in policy-making and ensure social and economic welfare for all citizens.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-5">
            <div class="row">
                <!-- Card 4 -->
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card">
                        <img src="images/fundamentalduties.jpeg" class="card-img-top" alt="Fundamental Duties">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h4 class="card-title">Fundamental Duties</h4>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                Fundamental Duties remind citizens of their responsibilities towards the nation and society.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Card 5 -->
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card">
                        <img src="images/unionstaterelations.jpeg" class="card-img-top" alt="Union and State Relations">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h4 class="card-title">Union and State Relations</h4>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                The framework defines the distribution of powers between the Union and State governments.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Card 6 -->
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card">
                        <img src="images/amendments.jpeg" class="card-img-top" alt="Amendments">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h4 class="card-title">Amendments</h4>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                Amendments ensure the Constitution evolves with the changing needs of society while maintaining its core values.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="text-center mt-5">
            <h3>Why Understanding the Framework Matters</h3>
            <p>
                A well-informed citizenry is the foundation of a strong democracy. Understanding the framework enables individuals to uphold their rights and fulfill their duties.
            </p>
        </section>
    </main>
	
	
	
</body>
</html>